posting_body: ['416 111th Street Court East, Tacoma, WA 98445', 'Monterra Apartments in Tacoma are conveniently located in the South neighborhood of Tacoma.', "With restaurants within walking distance, and shopping, schools, and parks nearby, you'll always find something to keep you busy at Monterra.", 'JBLM and the Tacoma waterfront are just a short drive away from the community.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Private Deck/Patio', 'Full-Size Washer/Dryer', 'Vaulted Ceilings On Top Floor Units', 'Spacious Breakfast Bars', 'Cozy Wood-Burning Fireplace', 'Walk-In Pantry', 'Community Features:', 'Reliable 24-Hour Maintenance', 'Garages Available', 'Fitness Center', 'Seasonal Outdoor Pool', 'Indoor Pool, Spa & Sauna', 'Lavish Cabana', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
